item.title: I need major help getting jdk, someone help?
item.dc:creator: @TeleNubby TeleNubby
item.description:
@TeleNubby wrote:

The batch file you have only checks for JDK versions up to 6u1. Instead of using that, simply use:

@echo off
"C:/Program Files/Java/jdk1.6.0_05/bin/javac.exe" *.java
pause
